---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import MediaText from '../components/MediaText.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import introPhoto from '../assets/images/engagedlearners.jpg';
import earlyPhoto from '../assets/images/outdoorplay.jpg';
import primaryPhoto from '../assets/images/collaborative-study.jpg';
import secondaryPhoto from '../assets/images/labsciencestudents.jpg';
import libraryPhoto from '../assets/images/librarysection.jpg';

const cardSizes = '(max-width: 820px) 92vw, 30vw';
---
<Layout
  title="Academics — Mt Cedar British International School"
  description="The British curriculum from Early Years to Secondary, taught in small, focused classes and adapted for our Nigerian context at Mt Cedar British International School, Benin City."
  active="academics"
>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">Academics</p>
    <h1>A clear path from first steps to school leaver.</h1>
    <p>The British curriculum, taught by caring teachers in small, focused classes, adapted thoughtfully for our Nigerian context.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<MediaText
  image={introPhoto}
  alt="Engaged Mt Cedar learners in a bright classroom"
  eyebrow="Our Approach"
  title="Where curiosity meets rigour."
>
  <p>At Mt Cedar, learning is active and personal. Small classes mean every child is known, challenged at the right level, and supported to reach further than they thought they could.</p>
  <p>We pair British academic standards with warm, attentive teaching — so pupils build not just knowledge, but the confidence and habits to keep growing.</p>
</MediaText>

<section class="academics">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head"><p class="eyebrow">Our Programmes</p><h2>Every stage, thoughtfully designed.</h2><p>Three connected stages that carry each child from playful early learning to confident, examination-ready study.</p></div>
    <div class="prog">
      <div class="pcard has-media">
        <div class="pcard-media"><Image src={earlyPhoto} alt="Young children at outdoor play" widths={[400, 640, 900]} sizes={cardSizes} format="webp" quality={72} loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="pcard-in"><div class="age">Ages 2–5</div><h3>Early Years</h3><p>A warm, play-led start where curiosity, language and confidence take shape through structured discovery.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="pcard has-media">
        <div class="pcard-media"><Image src={primaryPhoto} alt="Primary pupils in collaborative study" widths={[400, 640, 900]} sizes={cardSizes} format="webp" quality={72} loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="pcard-in"><div class="age">Ages 5–11</div><h3>Primary</h3><p>Strong foundations in literacy, numeracy and enquiry, with specialist teaching in the arts, science and sport.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="pcard has-media">
        <div class="pcard-media"><Image src={secondaryPhoto} alt="Secondary students in a science lab" widths={[400, 640, 900]} sizes={cardSizes} format="webp" quality={72} loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="pcard-in"><div class="age">Ages 11–16</div><h3>Secondary</h3><p>Rigorous, examination-ready study that stretches able minds and prepares students for the wider world.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<MediaText
  image={libraryPhoto}
  alt="The library at Mt Cedar British International School"
  eyebrow="Beyond the Textbook"
  title="A curriculum that goes further."
  reverse={true}
  background="var(--ivory-2)"
>
  <p>Reading, research and independent thinking sit at the heart of a Mt Cedar education. Our library and learning spaces give pupils room to explore ideas, follow their questions, and build a genuine love of learning.</p>
  <p>Specialist lessons in the arts, science and sport round out a broad, balanced education for every stage.</p>
</MediaText>

<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head"><p class="eyebrow">Why Mt Cedar</p><h2>How we teach.</h2><p>British rigour, small classes, and a genuine knowledge of every child.</p></div>
    <div class="feat-grid">
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="26" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M4 19V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13"/><path d="M6 17h12v4H6a2 2 0 0 1 0-4Z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>British Curriculum</h3>
        <p>Internationally recognised standards and progression, giving your child a portable, respected education.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="26" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><circle cx="9" cy="8" r="3"/><path d="M3 20a6 6 0 0 1 12 0"/><path d="M16 6a3 3 0 0 1 0 6"/><path d="M18 20a6 6 0 0 0-3-5.2"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Small, Focused Classes</h3>
        <p>Low pupil-to-teacher ratios mean lessons move at the right pace and no child is left behind.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="26" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M12 2 3 7v6c0 5 3.5 8 9 9 5.5-1 9-4 9-9V7l-9-5Z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Strong Pastoral Care</h3>
        <p>We know each learner as an individual, supporting wellbeing and character alongside academic progress.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="band">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow" style="color:var(--gold-bright)">Admissions Open</p>
    <h2>Find the right stage for your child.</h2>
    <p>Talk to us about your child’s year group and what a place at Mt Cedar could look like for your family.</p>
    <div class="cta">
      <a class="btn btn-gold btn-lg" href="/admissions">Apply for a Place <span class="arr">→</span></a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg" href="/contact">Ask a Question</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
